n </span>Menu <span class=\"expicon glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down\"></span></button>\n<ul aria-orientation=\"vertical\" data-ajax-replace=\"/content/dam/canada/sitemenu/sitemenu-v2-en.html\" role=\"menu\">\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/jobs.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Jobs and the workplace</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/business.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Business and industry</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/benefits.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Benefits</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/health.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Health</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/taxes.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Taxes</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/environment.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-offset-6 col-xs-6 col-md-offset-0 col-md-4\">\n<section id=\"wb-so\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Sign in</h2>\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/pr-portal.html\"><span class=\"visible-xs\">IRCC sign in</span><span class=\"hidden-xs\">IRCC sign in</span></a>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada.html\">Live in Canada</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship.html\">Sponsor your family members to immigrate to Canada</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwstitle section\">\n<h1 dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">\nSponsor your parents and grandparents</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div data-wb-jsonmanager='{\n\t\"url\": \"/content/dam/ircc/documents/json/fees.json\",\n\t\"name\": \"fee\"\n}' id=\"jsonmanagerfees\"></div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-7\">\n<p>This is a program to sponsor your parents and grandparents to become permanent residents of Canada.</p>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\">\n<h2 class=\"h3\">New Ministerial Instructions for the Parents and Grandparents Program come into effect January 1, 2026</h2>\n<p>These administrative steps allow us to keep processing existing applications into 2026. Details on the next intake will be shared on our website and <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/news/social-media.html\">social media channels</a> as soon as they are available.</p>\n</div>\n<h2>2025 intake</h2>\n<p>Starting July 28, 2025, we invited potential sponsors who submitted an interest to sponsor form in 2020 to apply for the 2025 intake.</p>\n<p>We sent 17,860 invitations over approximately 2 weeks. Our goal is to accept 10,000 complete applications.</p>\n<p><strong>The last day to apply was October 9, 2025.</strong> We’re no longer accepting applications.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-5 pull-right mrgn-tp-md\">\n<section class=\"well brdr-rds-0 position-relative\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-2 col-lg-3\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"/content/dam/ircc/images/icons/traffic-light-outline.svg\"/></div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-10 col-md-8 col-lg-9\">\n<p class=\"mrgn-bttm-0 mrgn-tp-sm\"><strong>Status</strong></p>\n<p class=\"mrgn-bttm-0\"><strong>2025 intake</strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"label label-danger\">Closed</span><br/>By invitation only</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"well brdr-rds-0 position-relative\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-2 col-lg-3\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"/content/dam/ircc/images/icons/ptclock.png\"/></div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-10 col-md-8 col-lg-9\">\n<p class=\"mrgn-bttm-0 mrgn-tp-sm\"><strong>Processing times</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-processing-times.html\">Check processing times</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"well brdr-rds-0 position-relative\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-2 col-lg-3\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"/content/dam/ircc/images/icons/feesdollar.png\"/></div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-10 col-md-8 col-lg-9\">\n<p class=\"mrgn-bttm-0 mrgn-tp-sm\"><strong>Fees</strong></p>\n<p>Starting from <span data-json-replace=\"#[fee]/fc-pgp-rprf/en\">Error loading fee. <a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/information/fees/fees.asp\">Check the fee list</a>.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-7\">\n<details>\n<summary><strong>If you were not invited to apply to sponsor your parents and grandparents</strong></summary>\n<p>Your parents and grandparents may be eligible to apply for a <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/parent-grandparent-super-visa/eligibility.html\">super visa</a> which lets them stay in Canada for 5 years at a time.</p>\n<p>Parents and grandparents visiting on a super visa can also apply for 2-year extensions to their stay while they’re still in Canada.</p>\n</details>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-7 pull-left\">\n<nav class=\"gc-subway provisional\">\n<h2>Sections</h2>\n<dl>\n<dt><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/undertaking.html\">What it means to be a sponsor</a></dt>\n<dd>Understand your responsibilities as a sponsor</dd>\n<dt><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/eligibility.html\">Check if you’re eligible</a></dt>\n<dd>Find out if you meet the requirements for sponsorship</dd>\n<dt><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/who-you-can-sponsor.html\">Who you can sponsor</a></dt>\n<dd>Find out who you can sponsor and if they’re eligible to come to Canada</dd>\n<dt><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/tell-us-you-want-sponsor-parent-grandparent.html\">Submit your interest to sponsor form</a></dt>\n<dd>How and when to submit your interest to sponsor form</dd>\n<dt><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/selected.html\">Find out if you’re invited to apply</a></dt>\n<dd>Each year, we invite potential sponsors to apply</dd>\n<dt><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/apply.html\">How to apply</a></dt>\n<dd>How and when to apply after receiving your invitation</dd>\n<dt><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/after-apply-next-steps.html\">After you apply</a></dt>\n<dd>What happens if we approve your application</dd>\n<dt><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/immigrate-canada/family-sponsorship/sponsor-parents-grandparents/prepare-arrival.html\">Settling in Canada</a></dt>\n<dd>What you need to know before and after your family members arrive in Canada</dd>\n</dl>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-8 col-md-9 col-lg-9\">\n<div class=\"wb-disable-allow\" data-ajax-replace=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/assets/feedback/page-feedback-en.html\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-12-29\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"